id":"19832b0e56f57a07cf695dcb9a90fd0bfac283a9","tid":505142,"uid":153209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T22:16:55.000Z","msg":"一開始話唔公開就已經有問題啦<br />\n樓主你都on9"},{"pid":"8082c990890092a00c575a784a4610e266d19d09","tid":505142,"uid":60171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T22:21:35.000Z","msg":"先唔講佢自己個人性格先，我睇得岀樓主你係完全因為為拍拖而拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為自己身在異鄉寂莫而且聖誕又到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起初又話當正常朋友唔做咩特別野，跟住個女仔叫到拍唔拍拖你就諗都無諗應承，咁講可唔可以話你完全係因為個女仔中意你所以你先中意返佢呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩個人係中意大家嘅話雙方都會至少略略感受到"},{"pid":"55e4367986bf7e0cf835b4a7997517c0342d1f38","tid":505142,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T22:23:56.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的<br />\n零分重作"},{"pid":"2ab6a6eccea42f81fc265df3061d59c757b2b634","tid":505142,"uid":117356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T22:36:04.000Z","msg":"綠帽最緊要除得快"},{"pid":"be28658b2fec8e97d0e2c66283cc2f0360036c01","tid":505142,"uid":74970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T22:37:37.000Z","msg":"ON9, 你同佢都係"}]}